Package dicomreader

DicomReader package contains classes needed by the application.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DicomReader
    The DicomReader class decodes Dicom files writing headers file and images files.
    DicomReaderGUI
    DicomReaderGUI class is the application's graphic user interface.
    LoadDict
    The LoadDict class opens the Dicom tags dictionary.
    ShowGPL
    The ShowGPL class is called by the DicomReaderGUI class to show the GNU General Public License to the end user.
